					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6035137#post-3827593</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6035137/scp-3446#post-3827593</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 07 Jun 2018 11:53:46 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Mortos</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1705184</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm a sucker for weird other dimensions, so I really like this. A couple of places where the language is a little clunky, but nothing that really detracts from the whole thing.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">example</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <blockquote> <p>Recovered specimens are to be kept in a tank filled with the fluid from SCP-3446-1 and no light.</p> </blockquote> <p>Could be better worded as just &quot;kept in an unlit tank filled with&#8230;&quot;</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>Anyway, seems to me one of these coral things grow so big that it sealed the entire place within itself (the dome) and flooded the entire place.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6035137#post-3821282</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6035137/scp-3446#post-3821282</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 02 Jun 2018 13:53:12 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>IAmTheOoga</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3942052</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;AAAAAA</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Close, but remember, you could see sunlight through the dome, the dome was growing out from the column of the organism, and this place definitely seems as if a catastrophe had already happened&#8230;</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6035137#post-3820686</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6035137/scp-3446#post-3820686</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 02 Jun 2018 01:43:11 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Zzuxon</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1496981</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I liked this one quite a bit. +1.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;My&nbsp;interpretation..</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;close</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Someone built a giant concrete dome surrounding the entire planet to prevent a catastrophe resulting from these life forms having limitless access to light. How close am I?</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6035137#post-3820227</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6035137/scp-3446#post-3820227</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 01 Jun 2018 15:47:17 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>IAmTheOoga</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3942052</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Thanks! I personally didn't expect my exploration logs to be that good, because I was under the impression that I sucked at writing dialogue. Glad to know I was wrong! Have fun figuring out the ending. I did have an idea in mind when writing it, but it definitely isn't the only interpretation.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6035137#post-3820223</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6035137/scp-3446#post-3820223</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 01 Jun 2018 15:45:49 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>IAmTheOoga</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3942052</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It is meant to be a bit open to interpretation. I myself do have an interpretation and reason for writing it as such, but it is by no means the correct/only/official one.</p> <p>If you or anyone else figures out what I was gunning for, I'll be sure to let them know. In the meantime, feel free to brainstorm what you think it means. I love a good mystery, and I have discovered it's even more fun to provide the mystery!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
